sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as "ChatGPT/Claude.ai"
    participant LB as "Railway Load Balancer<br/>HTTPS Termination"
    participant MCP as "mcp-sse-server<br/>:8080 (public)"
    participant API as "memory-service<br/>:8001 (internal)"
    participant DB as "FalkorDB<br/>:6379 (internal)"
    
    Client->>LB: HTTPS request to<br/>mcp.up.railway.app/mcp
    LB->>MCP: HTTP to container :8080
    MCP->>MCP: getAuthToken(req)<br/>Extract API token
    MCP->>API: HTTP to<br/>memory-service.railway.internal:8001<br/>Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
    API->>API: require_api_token middleware
    API->>DB: Redis protocol to<br/>falkordb.railway.internal:6379
    DB-->>API: Graph data
    API-->>MCP: JSON response
    MCP-->>LB: Format as MCP JSON-RPC
    LB-->>Client: HTTPS response